item.title: Things I like....
item.description: I like… Python - I think this is a beautiful language. JavaScript - because you are pretty much required to know it anymore! BPMN Tools like Camunda because I can build as fast as I think, then adapt quickly. Docker and I need to learn Kubernettes… and when I am required too… * JAVA for work * .NET I used to use it (C# and VB.NET) I should mention that I also love Excel.
